ass. Therefore, at least some CGM clouds\nare exceptionally large and massive.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Jun 2015 18:11:46 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2015 23:09:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-16"}
