ange in excess of $\\sim$ 1 dex, a result which is\nstrengthened by the robustness tests we have performed. We suggest that the\nunderlying driver of the halo metallicity dispersion can be traced to the\ndiversity of galactic mass assembly histories inherent within the hierarchical\nclustering paradigm.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 13 Jun 2015 08:31:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-16"}
